description:
This is a free version of Blocked Traffic application with 80 positions (Easy and Medium levels).

Blocked Traffic application is a sliding puzzle game inspired by Nob Yoshigahara games. The goal of the game is to get a car on third line out of a grid full of automobiles by moving the other vehicles out of its way. Cars and trucks can only be moved within a straight line along the track. They can not be rotated. Cars can not also enter into construction areas. This application has 1000 game positions and 4 difficulty levels. It has 4 graphic themes (cars & blocks) This game also comes with solutions for all positions.
